00:13:59.479 --> 00:14:00.479
What an experience.

00:14:00.479 --> 00:14:02.479
This is a faith builder for Gideon.

00:14:02.479 --> 00:14:05.479
That's not really the focus of the message this evening.

00:14:05.479 --> 00:14:08.479
But we find that God is building Gideon's faith.

00:14:08.479 --> 00:14:10.479
And Gideon experiences this.

00:14:10.479 --> 00:14:12.479
