00:21:15.179 --> 00:21:17.279
What was that process?

00:21:17.279 --> 00:21:19.139
Help me understand.

00:21:19.139 --> 00:21:21.439
Unfortunately, I've never had anyone

00:21:21.439 --> 00:21:23.619
