00:21:43.759 --> 00:21:46.399
God has set forth, here's truth.

00:21:48.399 --> 00:21:49.599
Amen?

00:21:49.599 --> 00:21:51.579
Here's the way.

00:21:51.579 --> 00:21:53.739
We don't bargain with God.

00:21:53.759 --> 00:21:56.319
So we find that there's this announcement of peace.

00:21:56.319 --> 00:21:59.799
